    "Background": {
      "text": "Common cause of presentation to the ED, especially in adolescents\nThe majority of pediatric chest pain is benign and not cardiac in origin\nThe main cause of cardiac chest pain in pediatrics is\npericarditis\nFamily history plays an important part screening for familial history of sudden death",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
